LitCode 0.2.202 - Changes in TeX primitives, Introduction of plsty.py

* Basic TeX primitive like \\tt and \\it have been replaced with \\texttt{} and \\textit{}
* linit.py renamed to plsty.py. Source code is in plsty.web. This would be responsible for printing
  litcode.sty
* documentation/litcode.pdf is not getting deleted upon cleaning up the directory. This will allow people to
  read the source code without installing the package.